  02 Aug 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> ganeti-2.10.5-r4.ebuild,
  ganeti-2.11.6-r2.ebuild, ganeti-2.12.1-r3.ebuild, ganeti-2.12.3-r2.ebuild,
  ganeti-2.13.0-r2.ebuild, ganeti-2.14.1-r1.ebuild:
  Drop dev-haskell/deepseq depend. ghc bundles it for a long while and we are
  using that version.

